msgstr ""

#: src/1695-add-error-macro.md:51
msgid "Detailed design"
msgstr "詳細設計"

#: src/1695-add-error-macro.md:54
msgid ""
"The span given for the failure should be the invocation of the "
"`compile_error!` macro. The macro must take exactly one argument, which is a "
"string literal. The macro will then call `span_err` with the provided "
"message on the expansion context, and will not expand to any further code."
msgstr ""

